Docs.summary: Represents the configuration for an Out-of-Band (OOB) initiator in a ranging session.

remarks.para: Represents the configuration for an Out-of-Band (OOB) initiator in a ranging session. This class includes configuration options such as device handles, security level, ranging mode, and interval range for setting up an OOB initiator ranging session.
